_______________
In the One Hundred and Ninety-Fourth General Court
(2025-2026)
_______________
An Act relative to newborn infant safe sleep practices.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 Every Massachusetts hospital, through its maternity program, shall provide the parent or
2 parents or the legal guardian of a newborn infant with written informational materials containing
3 the American Academy of Pediatrics’ recommendations concerning safe sleep practices at the
4 time of such infant’s discharge from the hospital.
